schools.name: Science, Technology, Engineering, Arts, And Math Academy At La Presa

data.description: t’s hard to find a better view in San Diego than that of the homes situated high on Dictionary Hill. This 4 Bed 3 bath 2 car Garage home was fully remodeled last year with one of the walk in closets being turned into a massage room.  2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms are on the street level along with the kitchen and a giant deck that spans the length of the home access from the kitchen and a bedroom. Downstairs are 2 more bedrooms as well as the master bedroom with its own deck that shows off the amazing views.  Underneath the master bedroom on the ground level, is a spacious area for storage and another very large storage area can be accessed from the master closet/massage room as well as from the outside of the home.Termite Clearance recently provided by Mann VS Pest. $100,000 worth of upgrades, improvements and remodeling.
